{"id": 243315756, "title": "Miscreants attack police vehicle carrying accused in Karnataka, 4 cops injured", "text": "Four policemen were injured on Friday after miscreants intercepted a police vehicle and attacked officers while they were taking an accused to the police station in Karnataka's Gadag.The police officers, belonging to Gangavathi in Koppal district, were taking Amjad Ali, an accused individual, into custody. Ali's gang attacked the vehicle near a railway underbridge and shattered its window panes before fleeing with him, police said.The injured officers, ASI Shivasharana Gowda, Constable Mylarappa Sompura, Havaldar Marigowda Hosamani, and car driver Sharanappa Thimmanagouda, were admitted to a private hospital.Police used a private vehicle to pick up Ali, a resident of Gadag, when the incident occurred.\"The Gangavati Shahara police had come here to take an accused into custody in connection with a crime. They picked him up and left from there, after which they were attacked by the accused's gang. They also broke open the window panes of the vehicle. They managed to escape along with the accused,\" Gadag Superintendent of Police (SP) BS Nemagouda said.\"Four policemen suffered minor injuries. We will take action against all the accused as per the law based on their complaint,\" he added.Published By: Prateek ChakrabortyPublished On: Jun 29, 2024ALSO READ | 13 killed, many critical after bus rams truck in Karnataka's Haveri", "summary": "<a href=\"https://www.indiatoday.in/india/karnataka/story/karnataka-police-vehicle-attacked-accused-criminal-case-gadag-cop-injured-probe-2559970-2024-06-29\"> <img align=\"left\" hspace=\"2\" height=\"180\" width=\"305\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" src=\"https://akm-img-a-in.tosshub.com/indiatoday/images/story/202406/cop-vehicle-attacked-in-karnataka-292019229-16x9_0.png?VersionId=e_AUW5LjFTKM8XAAOaRu1BgC59S6swxu\"> </a> Miscreants attack police vehicle carrying accused in Karnataka, 4 cops injured", "url": "https://www.indi